<h2>Pricing</h2>

<p>
  Couple Joy's free tier limits how many questions you can answer; <strong>$29.99/year</strong> removes ads and unlocks unlimited questions and premium content. OurCouple starts with a <strong>7-day free trial</strong>, then a single <strong>weekly or yearly plan covers both partners</strong> — you don't each buy your own. If your relationship runs on the daily-question loop, Couple Joy's 3000+ bank is excellent. If you want a full shared space — couple card, games, memories — without paying twice, OurCouple's shared plan wins.
</p>

<h2>Privacy</h2>

<p>
  OurCouple encrypts your shared content end-to-end. Couple Joy does not advertise end-to-end encryption. For something as personal as your relationship, that's worth knowing — more on it in <a href="/blog/relationship-data-encryption">why your relationship data deserves encryption</a>.
</p>

